    <p>Thalyn is a scout of the Shadowfang Tribe, a whisper in the wind and a shadow in the undergrowth. Her dark eyes scan the world with a predatorâ€™s focus, and her lithe body moves with fluid precision through the densest forests.</p>
    <p>She specializes in the art of capture rather than killing. Her favored weapons are poison-tipped darts that strike from nowhere, sending foes into unconsciousness before they even realize they have been marked.</p>
    <p>A master of stealth and subtlety, Thalyn leaves almost no trace of her passage. To those she hunts, her presence is only a chill on the back of the neck and then nothing at all.</p>
    <p>Her loyalty to the Shadowfang runs deep, but she feels no particular attachment to her victims. They are tasks to be completed, not people to be pitied.</p>
